<!ATTLIST check result CDATA #IMPLIED>
<!ATTLIST check incr   CDATA #IMPLIED>

<!ELEMENT sequence (call+)>

<!ELEMENT change EMPTY>
<!ATTLIST change from  CDATA #REQUIRED>
<!ATTLIST change to    CDATA #REQUIRED>

<!ELEMENT code EMPTY>
<!ATTLIST code method  CDATA #REQUIRED>

<!ELEMENT variant ((account | call | change | check | choose | code | modulo | premod | product | sequence | set | test)+)>
